- rule_name: SANCT_ROUNDING_DIRECTION
  severity: Warning
  message: "SANCT_ROUNDING_DIRECTION: related financial functions use inconsistent rounding directions: `deposit` uses up, `withdraw` uses down, `claim_reward` uses down"
